<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-TW">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>🌸 名古屋・京都 8日遊 (修復版)</title>
<script src="https://www.gstatic.com/firebasejs/8.10.1/firebase-app.js"></script>
<script src="https://www.gstatic.com/firebasejs/8.10.1/firebase-database.js"></script>

<style>
  :root { --washi: #FDF6EC; --botan: #9B4B6B; --botan-dk: #6E2E49; --text: #3D2B1F; --border: #E8D5C4; --kin: #C8A84B; }
  body { font-family: sans-serif; background: var(--washi); color: var(--text); margin: 0; padding-bottom: 60px; }
  .app-header { background: var(--botan-dk); color: white; padding: 15px; text-align: center; position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 100; }
  .tab-bar { display: flex; background: var(--botan); position: sticky; top: 60px; z-index: 99; }
  .tab-btn { flex: 1; padding: 12px; border: none; background: transparent; color: white; opacity: 0.7; font-size: 0.8rem; }
  .tab-btn.active { opacity: 1; border-bottom: 3px solid var(--kin); font-weight: bold; }
  .panel { display: none; padding: 15px; }
  .panel.active { display: block; }
  .card { background: white; border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid var(--border); margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 15px; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); }
  .day-badge { background: var(--botan); color: white; padding: 2px 8px; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 0.8rem; margin-right: 5px; }
  .tl-item { margin-top: 10px; padding-left: 10px; border-left: 2px solid var(--border); }
  .editable:hover { background: #FFF9C4; cursor: pointer; }
  input { width: 100%; padding: 8px; margin: 5px 0; border: 1px solid var(--botan); border-radius: 4px; }
  .status-tag { font-size: 0.7rem; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.2); padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 10px; }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="app-header">
  <div style="font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: bold;">🌸 名古屋・京都 8日遊</div>
  <span id="sync-status" class="status-tag">📡 連線中...</span>
</div>

<div class="tab-bar">
  <button class="tab-btn active" onclick="switchTab('itinerary')">🗓 行程</button>
  <button class="tab-btn" onclick="switchTab('currency')">💴 匯率</button>
  <button class="tab-btn" onclick="switchTab('map')">🗺 地圖</button>
</div>

<div class="panel active" id="panel-itinerary">
  <div id="itinerary-content">正在讀取雲端資料，請稍候...</div>
</div>

<div class="panel" id="panel-currency"><div class="card">💴 匯率換算功能 (1 TWD = 4.62 JPY)</div></div>
<div class="panel" id="panel-map"><div class="card">🗺 地圖與常用地址</div></div>

